# Orca Slicer

Use [Orca Slicer Wiki](https://orca-slicer.com/wiki/) as the reference for:

- **Printer Settings**: K1C config, extruder, retraction, bed mesh
- **Process Settings**: Quality, strength, speed, support, multimaterial
- **Material/Filament**: Temperatures, flow, bed adhesion
- **Calibration**: Pressure advance, flow rate, input shaping, VFA

Project layout:
- `slicer/orca-slicer/printer/` — printer configs (K1C, Bambu, etc.)
- `slicer/orca-slicer/process/` — layer height, speed, support presets
- `slicer/orca-slicer/filament/` — PLA, PETG, and other material profiles
